      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-05-03T17:02:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "From what I can tell logdog uses grpc error codes to internally propogate if it should be returning 400\u0027s, 401s, 403s, 404s, etc.  If that\u0027s the case, this would be where it bubbles up to and turn into a user status code.",
      "parentUuid": "0affa020_d4d7a87c",
